data.description: DOUBLE LOT HOME, FENCED AND GATED!! CITY WATER! PARADISE! In Port Charlotte, Florida is waiting for you!   Visit this beautiful home, and FALL IN LOVE! Situated in the heart of town with easy access to all that's fun.  Do you GOLF?  Do you SWIM?  Do you play PICKLEBALL?  Do you FISH?  Do you love to BOAT?  Do you love BEAUTIFUL BEACHES?  If so, it just may be, that whatever you LOVE to do, is within easy miles of this location - MINUS the fees of an HOA and deed restrictions. This home has lovely, mature landscaping, and an EXTRA LOT that has been fenced and gated including the main property. The front entrance has a fully screened roomy front porch, easily a great place to unwind with a glass of wine - with beautiful glass double entry door opening into a huge great room - with pocketing sliders out to the pool area. Enjoy the the SALT WATER SOLAR heated pool and extensive lanai just waiting for you and your next get-together.  Kitchen has been upgraded and reconfigured, with granite countertops, wood cabinetry with soft-close drawers, and a built-in kitchen nook to enjoy morning coffee.  All flooring has been updated, tile and laminate.  Both baths have been upgraded with custom showers, granite counters, updated sinks and commodes.  The master EnSuite has a linen closet AND a huge walk-in closet. Master has a built-in shelf system for books or whatever you collect, along with space for flat-screen TV.  Master also has pocket sliders to the pool.  On the other side of this gorgeous home are 2 more bedrooms one of which has a murphy bed system, along with built-in desk and shelves.  The hallway has a huge linen closet, too.  The final bedroom is large with easy access to the 2nd bath - which also has an out-door to the extended lanai.  All rooms have ceiling fans, sometimes multiple fans, including the lanai.  Pool has been refinished.  If all this isn't enough there is a double-doored shed in the back of the property for all your extra tools!  Pool cleaner/creepy-crawly stays with home.  Washer and dryer stays.  The murphy bed  stays.  The roof, all soffits, and downspouts were replaced 2022 - wind mitigation report provided in attachments.  Garage has huge "attic space" with pull-down steps. AC serviced Oct 2023 and in excellent working condition per the AC company.  Septic pumped and checked Sept 2023 and deemed to be in proper working order, per the septic company. The EXTRA lot is deeded with the main property saving tax dollars.  Some photos are virtually staged.  MANICURED EXTRA LOT COMES WITH THIS GORGEOUS HOME - LOT FENCED AND GATED!
